hose children...and Nohr...\nDo you hold a grudge against them?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|I wonder. I would be lying if I\nsaid I forgave them. $k$p$E通常,|If I wanted to do something about it,\nmore than people's hearts...$k$pIt might be the country that's\ngrown terrible.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|I...see...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaWell, I've wrapped it for now.\nHow is it, can you walk?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaYes, somewhat...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|Then hold on to my shoulder.$k$pYou may not like it,\nbut bear with it for a while. $k$p$E通常,|Now, let's return to where the others are.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k
MID_支援_アクア_サイゾウ_Ａ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmサイゾウ|3$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|...Lady Aqua.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaAh, Saizou. What's the matter?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaI apologize for earlier.$k$pMore than just receiving treatment\nfrom you, I saw your old wound. $k$pIt's all my fault...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaI don't really mind...\nAre you honestly saying those things?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaYes. Many times, I thought\nI should apologize.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|Apologize...$k$pMore than that, isn't there\nsomething else you should be saying?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|Eh...? W-what do you mean by that?$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaI didn't particularly want an\napology when I helped you.$k$pThat's why, receiving an apology now,\nI'm not at all happy. $k$p$E笑,|Before apologizing, first what you should\nsay...are words of thanks, don't you think?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|!! I'm sorry...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaCome on, you're apologizing again.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,|Sor―No, that's...\nThank you. $k$pYou saved me without thinking about it...\nI'm grateful for that. $k$pBut even so, I should still apologize.$k$pNo matter how many times I\napologize it's not enough...$k$pfor all the inexcusable things I have said.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaFufu... Saizou, I'm astounded at\nhow stubborn you are...$k$pBut, it doesn't change the fact that to me,\nyou are an important comrade.$k$p$E通常,|If you're still thinking of\napologizing to me...$k$pFrom now on, will you be a little\nless distant from me?$k$pI also haven't been good at that, but...$k$pAs much as possible,\nI'll put in the effort as well.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes... Of course.$k$pI believe in you as a comrade,\nso from now on I swear to fight with you.$k
MID_支援_アクア_サイゾウ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmサイゾウ|3$w0|$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,|...Lady Aqua.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Saizou... This again?\nI've already said I don't mind.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaNo. Having seen a lady's scars, I wish for\nyou to let me help you in some way.$k$pIn our village, there is a medicine that can\nheal old scars with no trace left behind.$k$pI have it with me now.\nWill you use it?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E通常,|No. I appreciate the sentiment but...\nIf you have such a thing...$k$p Please have someone else use it.$k$pSpeaking of old scars... Isn't the one over\nyour eye quite deep as well?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,|This is...\nA wound that I must bear.$k$pHealing it...\nMy soul would not allow such a thing.$k$pOn top of that... Between women and men\nscars have a different significance, no?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|You're... a bit chauvinistic, aren't you?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,|I... cannot deny that.$k$pEven so, I wish to take responsibility\nfor having seen your scar...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|Responsibility...?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E怒,照|Lady Aqua... Please be lovers with me.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,照|Eh...!?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E通常,照|Having been touched by your kindness\nand having seen your scar...$k$pI wish to protect you from this day onwards.$k$pTruly, from the bottom of my heart.$k$pOf course, as a shinobi, I have made my\nmind to follow Master Ryouma but...$k$pNow... As a man, I have decided in my\nheart that I wish to protect you.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,照|Do you... also mean that in atonement for\nnot having trusted me til now?$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E苦,照|I... do not know.$k$pHowever, my atonement, your scar,\nall of it... makes me find you dear to me.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E通常,照|Saizou...$k$p$E笑,照|…………$k$p... Thank you. For having trusted in me\nand for loving me... I'm so happy.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$Wa$E笑,照|T-then...!!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑2,照|Yes. I have no reason not to love\nsomeone who loves me so much.$k$pLet us be together.$k\n$Wsサイゾウ|$WaThank you so much, Lady Aqua.\nI will protect you with everything I have...!$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaYes. As will I.$k
